{"tid":1384419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲杯葛搵TVB藝人賣廣告嘅商戶","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:09:31.000Z","uid":113630,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9b26a0462b450b270e0633ba231fb62c64089bb0","tid":1384419,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"追擊商場活動同杯葛廣告商戶都漸見成效，係時候發起進一步打擊TVB收入嘅行動<br />\n除咗電視廣告外，依家藝人可以透過自己IG FB 出 post 賣廣告賺錢，TVB可以從兩者抽取收入<br />\n第一個攻擊目標應該係搵陳凱琳賣廣告嘅公司，因為一來佢產後多咗廣告賣，二來以陳小姐同佢老公嘅家底，呢啲錢都係賺錢買花戴啫，無謂影響到其他生活條件較差嘅藝人<br />\n雪花秀：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vzf59K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vzf59K.jpg&h=eada8795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電郵：sulwhasoo@amorepacific.com.hk <br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Sulwhasoo.HongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSulwhasoo.HongKong%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=baa8edd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Sulwhasoo.HongKong/</a><br />\n施華洛世奇:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPMKe25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPMKe25.jpg&h=5e1d7495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電郵：<a href=\"http://customer_relations.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcustomer_relations.hk&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=889c1716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">customer_relations.hk</a>@swarovski.com <br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SWAROVSKI.global/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSWAROVSKI.global%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=37b704d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SWAROVSKI.global/</a><br />\nLancome:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXy1hgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXy1hgq.jpg&h=f25f021c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電郵：<a href=\"https://www.lancome.com.hk/zh_HK/contact#contact-us-form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lancome.com.hk%2Fzh_HK%2Fcontact%23contact-us-form&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=1f1a704e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lancome.com.hk/zh_HK/contact#contact-us-form</a><br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lancomehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flancomehk%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=dfcdeb24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lancomehk/</a><br />\n請勸喻以上商戶唔好再俾錢TVB賺，否則呼籲杯葛"},{"pid":"da674baa5934c9666944bc96792f882826f5634a","tid":1384419,"uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"8.5 全港罷工"},{"pid":"93cf1c6eff1f75bbb5427353388ea49d8c69db6c","tid":1384419,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"陳凱林查身咁撚樣衰都應該要杯葛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb83e4d59ee2e920078c35868e7d47db02f9f0c","tid":1384419,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f29423bf374e03dfc735c28dcb0ea2baf1f9b132","tid":1384419,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:50:16.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394f0efe95e611d47ec0e88e9dc5fe2b199d9a43","tid":1384419,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"df66f9182c68e167a9f392a700d7e53bc51f6c1e","tid":1384419,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply